        <item>
            <title>Nothing 品牌 DIY 手機 CMF Phone 1     硬件規格+售價+開賣日期</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/cmfphon1-released-hk-price-and-date/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cmfphon1-released-hk-price-and-date</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/cmfphon1-released-hk-price-and-date/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 12:00:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[買物情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CMF Phone 1]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nothing]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1248816</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Nothing 旗下的子品牌 CMF 終於正式推出其第一部手機 CMF Phone 1，這款 Android 手機採用了相當卓越的硬件，並以高度可定製的模組化設計為賣點。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248823 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-5-694x414.jpg" alt="CMF Phone 1" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-5-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://cmf.tech/en-hk/pages/phone-1">Nothing（United Kingdom）</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">CMP Phone 1 使用了 MediaTek 的天璣 7300 8 核心晶片，具有 6.67 英吋的 FHD 120Hz AMOLED 屏幕，採用 5000 萬像素的主鏡頭和 200 萬像素的人像感光鏡頭以及 1600 萬像素的前置鏡頭。CMP Phone 1 電池容量為 5000 mAh，一次充電的電量足以使用兩日。香港將發售配備 8GB RAM 和 256GB ROM 版本，將支援 Wi-Fi 6、Bluetooth 5.3 和 9 波段雙 5G 但未有支援 NFC 和無線充電功能。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248821 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/nothingcmfphone1-694x390.jpeg" alt="CMF Phone 1" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/nothingcmfphone1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/nothingcmfphone1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248822 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/nothingcmfphone-694x390.jpeg" alt="CMF Phone 1" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/nothingcmfphone-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/nothingcmfphone.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/07/08/nothing-debuts-cmf-phone-1-modular/?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR3ikyn8zCz8bdNMvFXLf9BzgFZWpUSD4H8XhUtRdT0mHhaYW66j-LeWfKc_aem_HsiOAYDyUDAGSxEoZK5aZw">MacRumors</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">這款手機其中一個最大賣點是其 DIY 元素，用户可以更換機身背板又或者添加配件。CMF Phone 1 向用户提供平頭螺絲批和螺絲來更換不同顏色的外殼和安裝配件，香港 Nothing 官網亦列出 CMF Phone 1 的綠、黑、橙及藍色機殼，腳架配件、手機繩及卡片套等，但價格仍有待官方公佈。CMF Phone 1 將會在香港 7 月 12 日開始發售，有黑色和綠色兩個選擇，建議售價為 2299 港幣。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/07/08/nothing-debuts-cmf-phone-1-modular/?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR3ikyn8zCz8bdNMvFXLf9BzgFZWpUSD4H8XhUtRdT0mHhaYW66j-LeWfKc_aem_HsiOAYDyUDAGSxEoZK5aZw">MacRumors</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.businesstoday.in/technology/news/story/nothing-cmf-phone-1-launch-today-expected-price-specifications-design-other-details-436180-2024-07-08">Business Today</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/cmf-by-nothing-buds-pro-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】cmf by Nothing Buds Pro　外形　佩戴感　音質　降噪　功能開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/cmf-by-nothing-watch-pro-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】cmf by Nothing Watch Pro　外形　佩戴感　功能　屏幕　操控體驗　使用時間開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/nothing-ear-a-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Nothing Ear (a)　外形　佩戴感　音色　功能　使用時間開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/cmfphon1-released-hk-price-and-date/mobile-phone/">Nothing 品牌 DIY 手機 CMF Phone 1     硬件規格+售價+開賣日期</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
