        </item>
        <item>
            <title>支付寶推 NFC「碰一下支付」     全中國超過 2300 個品牌試行</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/alipay-3/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=alipay-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/alipay-3/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1248724</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">支付寶在開放日活動中宣佈全新付費方式「碰一下支付」。相比傳統的「掃一下支付」，「碰一下支付」更加方便快捷，用户只需解鎖手機並碰一下收款裝置，即可完成付費，無需進入支付寶 App 點擊付款碼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248726 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-3-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-3-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用户只需解鎖手機並碰一下收款裝置，即可完成付費（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/780/382.htm?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2wx7IO9r43DKqLnxzV1t2xOII8QoCML7n6HMx-RzAqX47xXCSMFiVI1jU_aem_BVI-MlwwQI55YMXDOCCgxQ">IT 之家</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong> </strong></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「碰一下支付」利用了手機的 NFC 技術，在手機解鎖和 NFC 開啟狀態下，只需將手機靠近付費裝置，即可自動跳轉至確認頁面，完成付費。過程省去傳統「掃一下支付」所需的多個步驟。付費裝置分為手持和枱式兩種造型，適用於不同店鋪的需求，並內置 4G 網絡，無需依賴 Wi-Fi。「碰一下支付」兼容適配了包括鴻蒙、Android、iOS 在內的多種系統，亦支援銀行卡、支付寶餘額、餘額寶、花唄、小荷包等多種付費方式。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248727 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-4-694x556.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="556" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-4-694x556.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-4.jpg 1123w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248734 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-5-684x580.jpg" alt="" width="684" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-5-684x580.jpg 684w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-5.jpg 1061w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 684px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「碰一下支付」已在全國多個地方使用（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/780/382.htm?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2wx7IO9r43DKqLnxzV1t2xOII8QoCML7n6HMx-RzAqX47xXCSMFiVI1jU_aem_BVI-MlwwQI55YMXDOCCgxQ">IT 之家</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong> </strong></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「碰一下支付」已經在上海、成都、武漢、長沙、杭州、福州等六個城市的超過 2300 個品牌及商家中試行，包括紅旗、美宜佳、7-11、十足、逸刻、良品鋪子等便利店，以及大型商場及社區，如上海靜安大悦城、成都萬象城、龍湖杭州濱江天街等。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/780/382.htm?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2wx7IO9r43DKqLnxzV1t2xOII8QoCML7n6HMx-RzAqX47xXCSMFiVI1jU_aem_BVI-MlwwQI55YMXDOCCgxQ">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/07/sams-club-to-hongkong/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國山姆超市今日起可直送香港　現接受 Alipay HK、支付寶、微信支付</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/alipay-3/fun-tech/">支付寶推 NFC「碰一下支付」     全中國超過 2300 個品牌試行</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
